profile:
Lambton County and surrounding area has a brand new local Pest Control Company offering the most competitive rates you will find. We have the best qualified local technicians who know the area, the pests and the remedy.

Try us this season and see the difference local makes. Show us a competitors bill for last years services and we will beat it by 20%!
